data.description: The charming Pecan plan is located within the community of Bunton Creek Village and features thousands of dollars in upgrades. This new 1-story home includes 3 bedrooms and 2 baths. Upgraded features included in the Pecan are energy-efficient kitchen appliances including refrigerator, granite countertops, designer wood cabinets and an attached two-car garage. The Pecan also showcases a master suite with a walk-in closet, as well as a fully fenced backyard, covered entryway and front yard landscaping.
